ivardefs.name: entity
ivardefs.desc: A reference to the entity that is a member of the group. Must be consistent with Group.type.

ivardefs.name: inactive
ivardefs.desc: A flag to indicate that the member is no longer in the group, but previously may have been a member.

ivardefs.name: period
ivardefs.desc: The period that the member was in the group, if known.

properties.desc: Identifies the resource instances that are members of the group.
